description: Are you bored and looking for a show to watch? Just ask this app for a suggestion!  You'll get a show, a short description, and also where the show is available - Amazon Prime Video, Netflix, HBO, etc.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, Ask bingeable shows for a show
Alexa, Ask bingeable shows to tell me a show to watch
name: Bingeable TV Shows
shortDescription: Ask me to suggest shows to binge watch!
